Package com.team6133.lib.util.drivers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CANTalonFactory
    Creates CANTalon objects and configures all the parameters we care about to factory defaults.
    CANTalonFactory.Configuration
    Configuration class that manages all of the default configurations for the Talon SRX.
    IRSensor
    Driver for an analog Sharp IR sensor (or any distance sensor where output voltage is a function of range, really).
    LazyCANTalon
    This class is a thin wrapper around the CANTalon that reduces CAN bus / CPU overhead by skipping duplicate set commands.
    LidarLiteSensor
    Driver for a Lidar Lite sensor
    MA3AnalogEncoder
    A 10-bit analog MA3 absolute encoder.
    MA3Encoder
    A 12-bit PWM MA3 absolute encoder.
    MB1043
    Driver for a MB1043 ultrasonic sensor
    NavXmicro
    Driver for a NavX board.
    RevDigitBoard  
    RevRoboticsAirPressureSensor
    Wraps an analog input for a Rev Robotics Analog Pressure sensor.
    UltrasonicSensor
    Driver for an analog Ultrasonic Sensor (mainly to help smooth out noise).
